foreign_born.label: Foreign born
foreign_born.desc: Percentage of residents who were not U.S. citizens at birth

poverty.label: Poverty rate
poverty.desc: Percentage of people in households with income below the poverty level

deep_poverty.label: Deep poverty rate
deep_poverty.desc: Percentage of people in households with income at or below 50 percent of the poverty level

cost_burden.label: Housing cost burdened
cost_burden.desc: Percentage of households spending more than 30 percent of their income on housing

hh_income.label: Household income
hh_income.desc: Combined income from all members of a household 15 years old or older

homeownership.label: Homeownership
homeownership.desc: Percentage of households owned by the head of household

labor_force.label: Labor force participation rate
labor_force.desc: Percentage of people in the military or classified in the civilian labor force

unemployment.label: Unemployment rate
unemployment.desc: Percentage of the civilian work force that is unemployed

disability.label: Disability
disability.desc: Percentage of people with a disability (civilian noninstitutionalized population)

commute.label: Commute to work
commute.desc: Percentage of workers who commute to work

pre_K.label: Preschool enrollment rate
pre_K.desc: Percentage of preschool-aged children enrolled in preschool

homicide_capita.label: Homicide rate
homicide_capita.desc: The number of homicides per 100,000 inhabitants
